OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780049132
OL,3,CUnmarked police car rams dangerous
OL,4,Cdriver in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,FWatch: Unmarked Sussex Police car rams
OL,7,FVolkswagen Golf during high-speed
OL,8,Fpursuit.
OL,10,FFootage has captured a high-speed
OL,11,Fpursuit showing officers from Sussex
OL,12,FPolice ramming a dangerous driver who
OL,13,Fwas travelling at twice the speed
OL,14,Flimit in Crawley.
OL,16,FOfficers were on patrol in an unmarked
OL,17,Fcar when they spotted a Volkswagen
OL,18,FGolf undertaking other vehicles and
OL,19,Fdriving at speed. The Golf pulled
OL,20,Fover, but then sped off when the
OL,21,Fpolice tried to speak to the driver.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
