FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780049132
OL,3,CUnmarked police car rams dangerous
OL,4,Cdriver in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,FCarlos Diago Silva, the 25-year-old
OL,7,Fdriver from Bewbush, reached speeds of
OL,8,F100 mph in a 50mph zone and 80mph in a
OL,9,F30mph zone. He then ran a red light
OL,10,Fand went the wrong way around two
OL,11,Froundabouts.
OL,13,FDashcam footage shows the police
OL,14,Framming Silva's car to bring it to a
OL,15,Fstop.
OL,17,FSilva then fled the scene on foot, but
OL,18,Fwas quickly identified after he left
OL,19,Fhis mobile phone and a McDonald's
OL,20,Freceipt in the car, which was
OL,21,Fcorroborated by CCTV evidence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780049132
OL,3,CUnmarked police car rams dangerous
OL,4,Cdriver in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,FSilva was arrested and charged with
OL,7,Fdriving while disqualified, dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving and driving with no insurance.
OL,10,FHe pleaded guilty to all offences at
OL,11,FLewes Crown Court on 7 May and was
OL,12,Fsentenced to 14 months in prison. He
OL,13,Fwas also banned from driving for three
OL,14,Fand a half years.
OL,16,FInspector Ollie Pullen, of the
OL,17,FSpecialist Enforcement Unit, said:
OL,18,F"Silva made a conscious decision not
OL,19,Fto stop for police, knowing he was
OL,20,Fdisqualified from driving and should
OL,21,Fnot have been behind the wheel.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780049132
OL,3,CUnmarked police car rams dangerous
OL,4,Cdriver in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,F"What followed, and what the footage
OL,7,Fshows, is some of the worst driving I
OL,8,Fhave seen, placing members of the
OL,9,Fpublic at significant risk."
OL,11,FHe added: "I am pleased that the court
OL,12,Frecognised the seriousness of this
OL,13,Foffending and reflected it in the
OL,14,Fsentence imposed. Despite running from
OL,15,Fthe vehicle, he was traced through
OL,16,Fforensic, CCTV and other enquiries.
OL,17,FFaced with that overwhelming evidence,
OL,18,Fhe ultimately pleaded guilty.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
