PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780049132
OL,3,CUnmarked police car rams dangerous
OL,4,Cdriver in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,F"In this case, officers used tactical
OL,7,Fcontact to safely bring the pursuit to
OL,8,Fa conclusion. Where it is necessary
OL,9,Fand proportionate, our officers will
OL,10,Fcontinue to use their training and
OL,11,Ftactics to protect our communities and
OL,12,Fcatch criminals."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
